%% Gambar IV.3 - SSD request GraphQL POST
%% Type: System Sequence Diagram.
%% Reference basis: Larman for SSD; UML 2.5.1; GraphQL Specification.
sequenceDiagram
    actor VU as k6 virtual user
    participant GQL as APE GraphQL system
    participant Schema as GraphQL schema/resolvers
    participant DAL as Shared DAL
    participant DB as SQLite corpus

    VU->>GQL: POST /graphql { query, variables }
    GQL->>Schema: parse, validate, execute query
    Schema->>DAL: get_image / get_track / get detections
    DAL->>DB: SELECT rows
    DB-->>DAL: rows
    DAL-->>Schema: dictionaries
    Schema-->>GQL: GraphQL data object
    GQL-->>VU: 200 {"data": ...} + X-Process-Time

    note over VU,GQL: POST route is not the cacheable APQ-over-GET path used in Phase 2 cache experiments.

